OL,5, Kate Garraway has described the        
OL,6, 'extraordinary bravery' of her children
OL,7, in her first appearance on ITV's Good  
OL,8, Morning Britain following her husband's
OL,9, death.                                 
OL,11,FSpeaking from home via video, she said 
OL,12,Fher family's "emotions are at 110%"    
OL,13,Fafter Derek Draper's funeral on Friday.
OL,15,FDraper died in January after living    
OL,16,Fwith extreme complications from Covid. 
OL,18,FThe TV host will return to hosting the 
OL,19,Fshow on Thursday, alongside Ben        
OL,20,FShephard.                              
